commit.message:
Migrate from nose to pytest as nose is now all but dead upstream

The `yield` mechanism is no longer supported in pytest, so this has been
replaced with `@pytest.mark.parametrize`. However, this means executing
the tests directly as `__main__` can no longer work.

Migrate from nose to pytest as nose is now all but dead upstream

The `yield` mechanism is no longer supported in pytest, so this has been
replaced with `@pytest.mark.parametrize`. However, this means executing
the tests directly as `__main__` can no longer work.
